skyproc

Class ModListing

  • java.lang.Object
    • skyproc.Record
      • skyproc.ModListing
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable

    public class ModListing
extends Record
implements java.lang.Comparable
    A more accurate representation of a modname: A combination of mod name without the suffix and its master flag. Skyrim.esm, for example, would be "Skyrim" with a true master flag.
    See Also:

      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(java.lang.Object o)
        Compare funtion is as follows:
        1) A master always is less than a non-master plugin
        2) The global patch always is greater
        3) A plugin that is on the active plugins list via importActivePlugins() comes before a plugin that was created manually.
        4) Remaining plugins are ordered in the same order they were created in the code.
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable
        Parameters:
        o - Another ModListing.
        Returns:
        Whether this modlisting is >/==/< the parameter.
